Step1: Install virtualbox
Step2: Install kubectl
       brew install kubectl
Step3: Installl minikube
       brew cask install minikube
Step4: Get one node kubernetes cluster up
       minikube start --vm-driver=virtualbox
Step5: Get the nodes
       kubectl get nodes
Step6: To stop the local kubernetes cluster, keeps the configuration
       minikube stop
Step7: To remove the local kubernetes cluster
       minikube delete
            
To get the current context
kubectl config current-context


       
       
